sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { Container, Typography, Box, Grid, Paper, Avatar } from '@mui/material'; import { styled } from '@mui/system'; import FeedbackIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Feedback'; import EngineeringIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Engineering'; import InsightsIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Insights'; import InterviewIcon from '@mui/icons-material/QuestionAnswer'; const CustomPaper = styled(Paper)(({ theme }) => ({ padding: '2rem', textAlign: 'center', backgroundColor: '#424242', color: '#ffffff', borderRadius: '12px', boxShadow: theme.shadows[3], '&:hover': { boxShadow: theme.shadows[6], transform: 'scale(1.05)', transition: 'all 0.3s ease', }, })); const About = () => { return ( {/* Header Section */} Welcome to AIQ 🤖 Revolutionizing Interviews with Cutting-Edge AI Technology {/* Mission Statement */} Our Mission 🚀 At AIQ, we are committed to transforming the interview process by using advanced AI technology. Our goal is to help candidates feel more prepared and confident by simulating interviews tailored to their resumes and job descriptions. We provide actionable feedback and personalized tips, empowering users to excel in their job search. {/* What We Offer Section */} What We Offer 💼 AI-Powered Interview Simulations Experience realistic interview simulations customized to match job descriptions and your profile, helping you practice and improve. Real-Time Feedback Get instant feedback on your responses, body language, and communication skills to help you refine your interview techniques. Data-Driven Insights Leverage analytics to gain deep insights into your performance and identify areas for improvement. Scalable Solutions Our platform is designed to support individuals and businesses of all sizes, providing scalable solutions for interview preparation. {/* Our Process Section */} Our Process 🔄 Upload Your Resume AI-Driven Analysis Get Personalized Feedback {/* Call to Action */} Join Us on the Path to Smarter Hiring 🚀 Ready to revolutionize your hiring process?{' '} Contact us today {' '} and let’s build the future of recruitment together. ); }; export default About;
